  <brief_title>Prevention of Hepatitis B Virus Reinfection After Liver Transplantation With Entecavir</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prevention of HBV Reinfection After Liver Transplantation Using Entecavir Monotherapy After Short-term HBIg Administration: A Pilot Study</official_title>
