  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether hepatitis B immunoglobin can be
      discontinued early after hepatitis B virus (HBV) induced liver transplantation and be
      replaced by the nucleoside analogue entecavir to prevent hepatitis B reinfection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
